<taxonomicName box="[924,1050,656,680]" class="Insecta" family="Aphodiidae" genus="Aphodius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="156" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dauricus">
<emphasis box="[924,1050,656,680]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="156">P. dauricus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but, due to the limited material at our disposal, it is maintained as a valid species.
</paragraph>
